Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-35,0:00:-02.-76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-74,0:00:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is this rain going to stop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp, have you got anything fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I've got a firework we\Ncould launch, but just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wanna do that?\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it. What if there's a\Nhostile ship nearby, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that book you've been\Nreading this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is showing interest in a book?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The book is called "Rainbow Mist,"\Nor "Niji no Kiri."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a novel, based on some\Nadventures this person had
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in an unusual region of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adventures, huh? That sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how bored he might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea sure is a strange place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I saw an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Will Make it Bloom!\NUsopp the Man and the Eight-Foot Shell"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's okay, right, Mommy and Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, keep close watch on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's a town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:04:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a small town, but it sure is lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to procure\Na few things here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, are you going to do some shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, get a load of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me there are wanted\Nposters! No, that's not it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a firework festival!\NAnd what's more, it's today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen fireworks in a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Nami-san, I shall be your escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh, no thanks. Mind your own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks, huh? I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you folks around before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you come to watch the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that isn't why--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, are these fireworks that well-known?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a famous festival on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been holding it\Nfor 400 years, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,400 years? That long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. You see that tower up\Non the mountain behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who live in that house\Nhave been making fireworks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for generations, since 400 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just an old man and a little girl\Nthat live there right now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then, does the old man\Nmake the fireworks by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! He makes them\Ntogether with the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They bang them out all\Nyear long, just for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it take a whole\Nyear to make fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dense! You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's all sorts of reasons. If I\Ntold you, you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, okay.\N--That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like we were\Nalmost out of gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'd share a little with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who knows?\N--I'll be back in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, I hope that nothing like\Nwhat went on last year happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what went on last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Last year, at the fireworks festival--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kadoyan! They came here\Nto have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to go out of your\Nway to tell them about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's nothing. Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! We should tell\NZoro and Robin about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's go tell Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, maybe we should eat first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how a firework\Nof my making turns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show this to them,\Nand they'll be so impressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and say, "if you're skilled enough\Nto make something this wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then please, take as much\Ngunpowder as you like, for free!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what a face you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really the head firework maker?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betcha! I'm Boss Odama,\Nthe pyrotechnist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'm begging you.\NYou can spare a little, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have lots of gunpowder, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any gunpowder\Nto give to a greenhorn like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:07:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, be on your way, please. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a minute! Please, decide if I'm\Na novice or not after looking at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fairly decent--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:08.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"14th generation Odama"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So round! So huge! So white!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission to\Ncome across my threshold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old-timer, is that real?!\NThat's papier-mâché, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would papier-mâché be doing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lying around a fireworks master's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for real. So, "this is a\Nfairly decent" what, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A three-gauge shell, huh?\NIt's pasted together a little loose,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's still pretty well put together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you hiding it?\NIt would be a waste not to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kodama, the granddaughter\Nof Grandpa Odama over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're the girl that makes fireworks\Ntogether with the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have you looking down\Non me, just because I'm little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still pretty skillful, maybe even\Nas much as Grandpa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ee-yow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go getting carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to\Ncontact the launch team!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did! They're going to be here\Nshortly to carry the shells away,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I would\Nget them out, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, you've got\Nto prepare the mortars,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get the wagon ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there, go give her a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why?\N--Just get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about? He tells me\Nto go away, then tells me to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up. I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fixing to slack off? Help me out, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not here to become an apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. I just came to\Nget some gunpowder from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had your own firework,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought for sure you\Nwanted to be an apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just made that one for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but I'm\Nnot up to working pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but it's true,\Nthat is well put-together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry up and finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to mention it, you said\Nthe same thing before, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? I thought\Nit was already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks only become finished\Nwhen they blossom beautifully
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why all of the fireworks in\Nthe storehouse are unfinished goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These launching mortars, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not finished until\Nthey're used as equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something amazing about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I told you. I won't have\Nyou looking down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, that ridiculously huge\Nfirework earlier is the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:10:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still unfinished, right? I sure\Nwould like to see that one go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, we tried to\Nlaunch one just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There was another one like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it didn't work.\NOur equipment was flawed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mommy and my daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They died, a year ago today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when the launch of the\N200-gauge shell went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This weather seems kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still hold the firework\Nfestival if it's raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's no use, Mommy, Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least get things ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's no use?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it clears up tonight, I'm planning\Non launching the 200-gauge shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Fireworks aren't food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't raise your voice, you dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't launch something\Nas huge as that on your own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I asked the launch\Nteam to help me out in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it already failed to launch\Nonce, right? It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to get the launch\Nteam folks caught in it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not. They'll just be\Nsetting it up, and then take cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of the launching by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"By yourself," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no! I'm telling your grandpa,\Nand putting a stop to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was going to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go ruining my\NMommy and Daddy's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Mommy and Daddy's dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our family has been making\Nfireworks for generations,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for over 400 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, that's okay...\N--Just let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, we once had the technical skill
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make and launch 200-gauge shells,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but at some point,\Nthat tradition was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:13:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my Mommy and Daddy's\Ndream to bring back that skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, tonight,\NI'm going to finish their dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second. Why would you\Njust blab something like that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to keep\Nyour grandpa occupied?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The launch team folks will be\Nhere soon to carry the shell away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While they're doing that,\Nkeep Grandpa occupied inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he doesn't come out here. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumb fool! How can I help you\Nout with something so dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:41.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"14th generation Odama"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because my Mommy and Daddy's\Ndream is still only half-finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to finish it for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A prayer before launching?\NA fine thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that isn't what you'll be launching.\NYou'll be doing smaller ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The launch team... Why did you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you say. They were\Nthinking of you when they told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! After all the begging I did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kodama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just too reckless.\NThat thing is sure to misfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know that for sure,\Ndo you?! I'm not afraid of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as though they don't know\Nhow those of us left behind feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what it means\Nto carry on their wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kodama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, well, we'll get things ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if you would, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you're getting ready,\Neven with the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rain will let up soon.\NThe wind is coming in from the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kodama is the only one\Nwho doesn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer, has that structure\Nbeen there the whole 400 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit upon a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about hearing me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are graves? Wow, they're funky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy and Daddy, like I said,\Nif this long spell of rain ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it means that I have your permission,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that I can launch the 200-gauge shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:16:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, does this mean I'm wrong, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It doesn't mean you're wrong. Kodama,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you launch your own fireworks,\Nwe'd be glad to stop the rain."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, Mommy and Daddy, your dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you think that's all our dream is?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You are our dream. Our dream\Nis that you will carry on for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become a fine pyrotechnist."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kodama, take your time, and\Nmake your own 200-gauge shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an unlimited\Namount of time, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kodama, if you can bring\Nback the 200-gauge shell,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that will also make our dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let Grandpa take care\Nof our 200-gauge shell;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:17:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you keep on showing us your\Nbeautiful fireworks up in heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, someday, I'll make my\Nown 200-gauge shell, you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thanks for understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, as promised..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a messenger, sent from heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp... Angel...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thank you! I'll try my best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is coming off nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I have to admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using the wheel on the\Ncart in the yard as a pulley,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he figured out the trick for dragging\Nthat thing out of the storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought that the\Ntower that's been here for 400 years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was actually the launch\Nplatform for 200-gauge shells...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is this kid, anyhow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"14th generation Odama"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes the rapid fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, outstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Last one!\N--Okay, last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that shabby firework just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how my first firework turned out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Old Man Odama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:21:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy and Daddy's firework...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to make a firework like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy and Daddy really were amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll be able to make\Na firework like that someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy! Daddy! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer, can I have some gunpowder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumb jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to catch a cold dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who catch colds are people\Nwho let their mind's guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.58,0:23:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wonder if someone\Nsomewhere is spreading stories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about Zoro, the pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never once called myself a pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fabled Pirate Hunter!\NZoro, the Wandering Swordsman"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
